   Crime Scene | A video widely circulated on social media shows a supposed police officer showing the damage caused by the bullets during the incident.
  
 
Mbele said one of the four men died on arrival at a Durban hospital.
“A 30-year-old victim succumbed to his injuries on arrival. Durban North police are investigating a case of murder and three counts of attempted murder. Three pistols were recovered from the scene,” she said. No arrests have been made.
Sunday Tribune